# Threads Directory

Store decision threads using the 6-stage causal flow.

## Structure

```
threads/
├── {type}/           # business, research, analysis
│   └── {thread-name}/
│       ├── meta.json
│       ├── 1-input.md
│       ├── 2-hypothesis.md
│       ├── 3-implication.md
│       ├── 4-decision.md
│       ├── 5-actions.md
│       └── 6-learning.md
└── index.md          # Thread registry
```

## Usage

- Each thread links to a goal
- Follow 6-stage causal flow
- Stage 6 learning updates Canvas
